source.name: Food Insp since Jan 2011
source.description: Health Department inspection results for food service establishments in King County, 2006 to the present. This data is organized by Business / Inspection Date / Violation. Each row in this dataset is an inspection, and if an inspection at a particular buiness results in multiple violations there will be multiple rows for that business with the same Inspection_Serial_Num. This dataset was last Updated on 11/02/2011 and is current from 1/1/2006 to 10/30/2011.
